  "text": "UAVs can also form an ad-hoc network to replace the malfunctioning tower in the cellular network. Once set up, the UAVs can act as mobile base stations and start routing traffic to and from the cell tower. However, due to their limited power sources, using UAVs is a temporary solution while trying to restart communication through the permanent networks [CITATION_1] .",
